title: War of the Roses: Diapers in the Garbage
description: Celeste was out of town at a bachelorette party over the weekend and when she got back she went over to her boyfriend's for dinner.  She was taking out the trash and then found something in the garbage can that shouldn't be there and when she asked him about it he claims that someone walking past must have put it in there but Celeste isn't buying it.
